These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, water, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, woodworking, skydiving
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking fanta##7
4. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | 7up       | iced-tea | fanta        |
| Hobby      | woodworking  | singing | skydiving        | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, fish, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, surfing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the owner of the fish##7
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | fish | rabbit       | hamster         | bird     |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | climbing | surfing | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, adventure, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, pop, jazz
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of metal and the fan of rock##7
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | adventure | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | pop | rock  | jazz   | metal |

