.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, photography, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cricket, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is singing##7
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | magic-tricks | singing       | photography |
| Sport   | cricket      | soccer   | ice-hockey | rugby  |

