.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, chess, writing, fishing
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indian, british, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the french is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
5. the french is on the left of the british##1
6. the indian is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing | traveling   | fishing | chess |
| Nationality   | turkish      | indian | french      | british |

