.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, iced-tea, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, australian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the indian##1
2. the indian is the person drinking tea##1
3. the french is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the australian##3
6. the australian is somewhere between the brazilian and the french##7
7. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | water      | iced-tea | tea     |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | australian | french   | indian |

