.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, garlic, papaya, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, french, american
1. the polish is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
4. the american is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating papaya##7
5. the french is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
6. the american is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | apricot   | garlic | papaya  |
| Nationality   | polish | french | american    | colombian |

