.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, turkish, german, indian
4 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, bird, lizard
1. the turkish is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the indian is the owner of the bird##1
4. the german is somewhere between the indian and the brazilian##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | indian | german | turkish | brazilian |
| Pet           | bird   | lizard    | cat       | turtle  |

