4. the chef is on the right of the fan of folk##1
5. the nurse is somewhere between the fan of folk and the paramedic##7
6. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
