.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, drama, musical, superhero
4 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, turtle, cat
1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the cat##7
2. the person watching drama movies is not the owner of the turtle##6
3. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person watching musical movies##6
4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the goat##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | superhero | drama | musical |
| Pet           | goat    | chinchilla   | cat  | turtle      |

