.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, spy, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, country, indie
1. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
6. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the person watching martial-arts movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | time-travel | martial-arts | spy   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | country      | disco      | indie |

