3. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is traveling##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
