.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, card-games, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person driving the airplane##6
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | dancing | rock-climbing | reading | card-games |
| Transport   | van   | quad-bike      | airplane        | motorbike  |

