The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, salsa, jazz, dubstep
1. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the fan of jazz##7
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person drinking milk is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | coffee   | sprite | milk | tea   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz   | dubstep | salsa |

