4. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
5. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the chef##7
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the dressmaker##1
7. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
