.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, bird, turtle, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, train, ship
1. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the owner of the bird##7
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | bird    | turtle | hamster     | rat |
| Transport   | train | ship  | jet-ski | subway |

 